name: W3ND-1 go()
description:
Patients claimed that these were possessed. No longer W3ND-1 units.
Executives called it an "Update Malfunction" and blamed IT.
This isn't a malfunction. 
The mannerism, the hiss, the stare. The clean cuts.
We heard of the myths. 
We just never thought it would manifest inside a machine.
Never thought it'd adapt and possess our creations rather than us.
We just made our own monsters. Our own graves.
